codex
I found the bridge schema on the in-flight U-M1 branch and will pin v4 to its exact field names. One important correction is required in the estimator: geometric prediction must exclude clocks, while the primary-clock and receiver-clock updates must each add their own drift through H·x; the current primary path omits that nonzero term.
